   Service Partners
   GOOGLE EXPERTISE

   AddApptr is one of the few members of Google’s Certified Publishing
   Partner (CPP) program. This means that AddApptr has access to many
   resources to improve management of Google products such as Google Ad
   Manager, the largest RTB exchange in the world. AddApptr can help
   publishers to optimize their set up of Google products in order to make
   sure that maximum results are achieved.
